description:
Beautiful trail behind the Chief. The trail has a lot of root, be careful when it's raining.
Follow the GPS trace.
directions:
Go up the stair at the beginning, follow the mark yellow.
Be carefull at the fork ! One trail go up to the top of the Chief on the left, the other on the right go to the direction of Squaw. Go on the right and follow the GPS trace.  Refer to other trail listings on this site describing the "Chief" main trail and access.
title: Stawamus Squaw
